{"tid":2428354,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"睡衣綁帶包不住！「兇版潤娥」溢出雪白巨球　下身春光狂洩","createTime":"2021-03-01T13:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T04:43:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"72867c575f42aeb28925439e2d89bf8ad84e3871","tid":2428354,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:04:00.000Z","msg":"南韓不少外型亮眼的DJ深受台灣男網友青睞，除了DJ SODA外，擁有姣好臉蛋、傲人上圍的DJ MIU，人氣同樣不遑多讓，更因甜美外型被封為「兇版潤娥」。從不吝嗇分享火辣福利的DJ MIU，近日特別在IG上PO出一張尺度破表的睡衣照，撩人姿態瞬間湧入大批粉絲朝聖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/30/2691268-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F30%2F2691268-PH.jpg&h=b2382e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓DJ Miu擁有甜美外型、魔鬼身材，是不少男粉絲心目中的夢幻情人。（圖／翻攝自DJ Miu IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/30/2691290-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F30%2F2691290-PH.jpg&h=7a6f502d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從照片可見，DJ MIU穿著布料超少的性感睡衣，兩條綁帶就快撐不住白皙雙球，兇猛弧形全都入鏡，往下一看，除了S纖瘦曲線吸睛外，下身還大開高衩露出零瑕疵腿根，私密地帶險些走光，讓人一看鼻血狂噴。她隨後將身體向後仰，誘人體態頓時更貼近鏡頭，惹火指數當場直衝天際。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/01/3045864-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F3045864-PH.jpg&h=32894bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼DJ MIU特別曬出自己的性感睡衣照，再度引發網友討論。（圖／翻攝自DJ MIU IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/01/3045865-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F3045865-PH.jpg&h=f3079414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n犯規視角照曝光後，粉絲紛紛留言猛誇，「建議有心臟疾病的男士別看，小心受不了」、「真的是越來越辣了」、「我支持妳再上傳10張」、「想當攝影師了」、「身材真棒，尤其配上甜美微笑，戀愛感噴發」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，DJ MIU人氣正持續竄升，IG已累積157.3萬追隨者，她每隔一段時間就會放送養眼福利，讓網友眼睛大吃冰淇淋；此外，DJ MIU先前到台北進行活動表演，還不忘拍下影片紀念，並說「來台灣太開心了，謝謝！」親民形象再度圈走一票粉絲的心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/08/2975539-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F08%2F2975539-PH.jpg&h=9d21ea04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲DJ MIU火辣不失可愛的模樣，為她帶來極高人氣。（圖／翻攝自DJ MIU IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/01/3045871-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F3045871-PH.jpg&h=d87babf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/01/3045870-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F3045870-PH.jpg&h=19f57439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/01/3045869-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F3045869-PH.jpg&h=f91d06d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc852aa850992204312d3950a4b12512852c42dd","tid":2428354,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"真版正啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兇版可以做玩具 性奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceee41663e7055d51fb0bb18215f52ccebb5e8d3","tid":2428354,"uid":73326,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:08:02.000Z","msg":"睇錯月娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243009135694279e85d79f1e7e0c67e059187489","tid":2428354,"uid":168366,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">屌你我唔係入黎睇士多啤梨</span>"},{"pid":"d26f572e6138190f74aa5c1a677d9ab57f8e83e5","tid":2428354,"uid":121095,"like":5,"d